name: 2021 Columbia Digital Storytelling Lab Breakthrough Award
description: (April 7, 2021) Series: “Digital Dozen: Breakthroughs in Storytelling Awards.“ Edition of one NFT, presented to DARKFIELD RADIO in recognition of its status as the most innovative narrative of 2020. http://digitaldozen.io/ award created by Lance Weiler @culturehacker, Marcio Lima, and Aaron Matys
